es.situm.sdk.v1

Annotation Type SitumDataManagerOptions


  • public @interface SitumDataManagerOptions
    SitumDataManager options

    • Field Detail

      • FORCE_DOWNLOAD

        public static final int FORCE_DOWNLOAD
        Force download from server. The value in the options map must be a boolean. Default value is false

      • CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER

        public static final int CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER
        Filter the result data by custom fields. The value in the options map must be a List of SitumSearchManager.KeyValueFilter Not used by default

      • CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER_MODE

        public static final int CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER_MODE
        Used with CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER. Set the filter mode if the list of filters has more than one filter. The value in the options map must be a SitumSearchManager.FilterMode. Default value is FilterMode.OR if CUSTOM_FIELDS_FILTER is set.
